            In a positive light, there is still a lot to play for, and by offering a differentiated opportunity focusing on cross-border sales, eBay could exploit a gap in the market that Walmart will not have the appetite to pursue. EBay doesnât state this, but in an ideal world, itâs going into its plans with its eyes open, and based on purchasing patterns itâs been seeing in and out of the country in recent years.

